OL,3,C'Swatting' hoax caller who faked
OL,4,Chostage situation sentenced
OL,6,FA British video gamer whose fake call
OL,7,Fto US police led to the shooting of an
OL,8,Finnocent man has been spared jail.
OL,10,FRobert Walker-McDaid, 28, from
OL,11,FCoventry, rang a US terrorism hotline
OL,12,Fin 2015 claiming he had plastic
OL,13,Fexplosives and hostages.
OL,15,FThe "swatting" incident led to a Swat
OL,16,F(special weapons and tactics) police
OL,17,Funit being sent to the home of Tyran
OL,18,FDobbs, who was shot with plastic
OL,19,Fbullets.
