OL,4,Chostage situation sentenced
OL,6,FWalker-McDaid had posed as Mr Dobbs,
OL,7,Fwho was shot in the face and chest and
OL,8,Fsuffered severe life-changing facial
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,F"Swatting" means making a hoax call
OL,12,Fabout a serious crime to emergency
OL,13,Fservices to incite panic and instigate
OL,14,Fthe deployment of an armed response
OL,15,Funit (Swat team) to neutralise a
OL,16,Fperceived threat.
