OL,4,Chostage situation sentenced
OL,6,FWalker-McDaid is the first person in
OL,7,Fthe UK to be charged over "swatting",
OL,8,Faccording to the Crown Prosecution
OL,9,FService, which worked with the US
OL,10,FDepartment of Justice and the FBI.
OL,12,FHe earlier admitted perverting the
OL,13,Fcourse of justice and was sentenced at
OL,14,FWarwick Crown Court on Friday to 20
OL,15,Fmonths in prison suspended for 18
OL,16,Fmonths.
OL,18,FHe was also ordered to complete 200
OL,19,Fhours of unpaid work and pay
OL,20,Fcompensation of #1,000 to Mr Dobbs.
