OL,3,C'Swatting' hoax caller who faked
OL,4,Chostage situation sentenced
OL,6,FZachary Lee, of Catsonville, Maryland,
OL,7,Fin the US, had met Walker-McDaid while
OL,8,Fplaying video games.
OL,10,FHe messaged him saying he needed
OL,11,F"someone swatted".
OL,13,FLee, who was jailed for two years in
OL,14,F2018 for his role in the crime, shared
OL,15,FMr Dobbs' address with Walker-McDaid,
OL,16,Fwho then called a Maryland terrorism
OL,17,Fhotline posing as Mr Dobbs.
OL,19,FHe told emergency services he was
OL,20,Farmed, was holding three people
OL,21,Fcaptive and had several bombs readied.
