OL,4,Chostage situation sentenced
OL,6,F"Walker-McDaid may not have intended
OL,7,Fto cause such serious harm, but by
OL,8,Fsowing panic and deceiving law
OL,9,Fenforcement into responding to a
OL,10,Ffictitious threat, he left an innocent
OL,11,Fman with life-changing injuries.
OL,13,F"British-based offenders who hide
OL,14,Fbehind online anonymity to commit
OL,15,Fserious crimes abroad will not escape
OL,16,Fjustice, and we will continue to work
OL,17,Fcollaboratively with international
OL,18,Fpartners to ensure perpetrators will
OL,19,Fface the full force of the law."
